name: USGS WaterWatch, Daily Streamflow Map, USA, 6.12.2008
description:
This dataset displays the average daily streamflow conditions for Thursday, June 12th, 2008 across the USA. The map depicts streamflow conditions as computed at USGS streamgages. The severity of the streamflows are represented by percentiles of historical daily streamflow for the day of the year. 

Percentage scale:
<10 = Much Below Normal Streamflow
10-24 = Below Normal Streamflow
25-75 = Normal Streamflow
76-90 = Above Normal Streamflow
>90 = Much above Normal Streamflow
